  constructor(private http: HttpClient) { }

  getScore(titleUrl) {
    return this.http.get(`${environment.url}cr/score/${titleUrl}`);

  }
```

2. Create a component that accesses that service and try to deconstruct the return value on the object.
import {DataService} from './data.service';

```
